        "content": "\u003cimg src=\"https://netsage-project.github.io/Science-Registry/netsage.png\"/\u003e\n\n\u003c!-- styling for the page --\u003e\n\u003cstyle\u003e\n.page-header {\nfont-weight: 800;\ncolor: #618ED0;\n}\nh1.title, h2.title, h3.title {\ncolor: #454545;\nfont-weight: bold;\n}\nh6.css-1ej1m3x-panel-title {\n  color: #454545;\n}\n\u003c/style\u003e",
