        "content": "\n\u003cfont color=\"#5794f2\"\u003e\n\u003cblockquote style=\"margin-top: 0px\"\u003e\n  \u003ch1\u003e\u003cb\u003eWelcome to Netsage - ACCESS \u003c/b\u003e\u003c/h1\u003e\n\u003c/font\u003e\nNetSage is an open privacy-aware network measurement, analysis, and visualization service designed to provide near real-time monitoring and visualization of R\u0026E data transfers. \nNetSage provides human-readable visualizations of normally opaque network data, helping ensure that scientific workflows are operating at maximum efficiency. \nNetSage services provide a combination of measurements, including SNMP and flow data, offering longitudinal network performance data visualization.\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nSelect one of the questions below to begin exploring!\n",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.5.5",
      "title": "",
      "transparent": true,
      "type": "text"
    },
